{"tid":2294673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"實驗室污染樣本誤把4的士司機評為陽性確診！再檢測後呈陰性　政府：未有證據出現交叉污染","createTime":"2020-11-21T08:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T14:33:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"47cf228b986f885e68b5be0889e2e45ce43e5d0f","tid":2294673,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561202-20201121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561202-20201121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM3yPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=ddfad6ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561202-20201121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0ecb7565\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561202-20201121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n4名職業司機早前經檢測後確診新型肺炎，入院後全部檢測樣本呈陰性，其後出院。政府發言人說，負責特定群組檢測計劃的金域檢驗，早前初步確認為1宗陽性及3宗「不確定」，按既定程序送往衞生署覆檢後，被確定為4宗陽性個案，當時的檢測結果顯示樣本的病毒含量極低，其後病毒檢測為陰性，獲安排出院，並不影響早前的確診個案定性。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，考慮到多宗個案同時被檢測為陽性，衞生署公共衞生化驗服務處早前進行跟進調查，包括向相關私營化驗所了解情況，視察實驗室和檢視樣本處理及化驗流程等，至今並未發現確實證據證明樣本於處理過程中出現交叉污染。<br />\n<br />\n公共衞生化驗服務處亦已根據實驗室質量管控規範，向化驗所提供建議，政府會繼續跟進，並密切留意化驗所為政府提供的服務水平，確保化驗質素有保證。"},{"pid":"49d371a3154c120f14d883d76b8430e1bdbbaabc","tid":2294673,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:02:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">實驗室乜名？<br />\n<br />\n唔敢開名？<br />\n<br />\n無記者問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a33758db1e52b5cf2dc4d463d5487218eea0601c","tid":2294673,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"強制檢測根本浪費時間<br />\n<br />\n經常有假陽, 假陰個案<br />\n<br />\n測試準確率從來不公布 (係咪準確率好低, 所以唔講?)<br />\n<br />\n實驗室求鬼其, 亂咁嚟, 仲要樣本污染！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d8f84ef93525102f8f057260cba89cc842e24a","tid":2294673,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49d371a3154c120f14d883d76b8430e1bdbbaabc","tid":2294673,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:02:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">實驗室乜名？<br />\n<br />\n唔敢開名？<br />\n<br />\n無記者問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"蘋東開左名"},{"pid":"7b2c06c9ebd7cf9779531c86ba27f08fac5d6334","tid":2294673,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49d371a3154c120f14d883d76b8430e1bdbbaabc","tid":2294673,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:02:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">實驗室乜名？<br />\n<br />\n唔敢開名？<br />\n<br />\n無記者問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"支那實驗室嚟"},{"pid":"aec97616c0ca675b05fe1b06f9cebc4306367586","tid":2294673,"uid":66049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49d371a3154c120f14d883d76b8430e1bdbbaabc","tid":2294673,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:02:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">實驗室乜名？<br />\n<br />\n唔敢開名？<br />\n<br />\n無記者問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"補埋link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/42BXNGN7HJCIDJMRBVE5VYYJOU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F42BXNGN7HJCIDJMRBVE5VYYJOU%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM3yPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=85b4ec33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F